des:
HYPNOTEK products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to your HYPNOTEK products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "HYPNOTEK" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one tuya account in our "HYPNOTEK" app;
(3). You need to have some HYPNOTEK devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "HYPNOTEK" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Hypnotek smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Hypnotek smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Hypnotek smart", and you'll be navigated to "Hypnotek smart" login page;
(9). Input your HYPNOTEK account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
